data.description: Wow! This home will not disappoint you! Move in ready with everything you need. Gorgeous 18'' tile throughout, granite counters and island in kitchen, open floorplan with soaring ceilings to the roof. Also features a wet bar in the living room to entertain your family and friends. Two bedrooms with one bath downstairs, four bedrooms and two bath upstairs along with a giant loft/game room. Three car garage with side exit, rv gate with poured pad on the side of the house. Back yard is an entertainers dream with a grass area, cool decking, built in bbq and amazing gas fireplace for those chilly nights. And for those hot days a beautiful heated pool and spa. Don't miss this one....won't last long! Not lender owned or short sale. Answer within 24 hours or less.
